dc_title_s: Settsu no Kuni Ōsaka-fu kubun shin saizu; Hashimoto Chōgetsu hen.; Ōsaka-fu kubun shin saizu
dc_description_s: Copperplate print. Oriented with north to the left. Relief shown pictorially. Includes distance chart, and lists of town names. Includes 2 insets: 1. Kyōto -- 2. Settsu no Kuni zen ryakuzu. 1 map: col.; 48 x 72 cm., folded in covers 17 x 13 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
